highlights.text: KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Malaysia. “Golden” is the highest at #31.
“零距离的思念” by TINY 7 has been on Viral Songs Malaysia the longest, at 156 days straight.
“Vizhi Veekura - From "Think Indie"” by Sai Abhyankkar, Sai Smriti, and Adesh Krishna is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Malaysia, up 28 spots at #59.
“Perfect Pair” by R.L. Beats is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Malaysia at #61.
